description:
Angela: Asgard's Assassin Volume 1

An Avengers Now! series. After the events of Original Sin, the former Guardian of the Galaxy receives her very own ongoing series in which she is on a quest to find out more about herself. The series lasted only 6 issues due to the events of Secret Wars and was replaced by the Secret Wars tie-in mini-series 1602 Witch Hunter Angela. After Secret Wars, she received a new ongoing series named Angela, Queen of Hel.

Collected in Angela: Asgards Assassin - Priceless.

Translated into German and Spanish.
name: Angela: Asgard's Assassin
